CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 23, 1952, pg. 15, reads: "Baby Corner ... Cute little Conchita Carmen Garcia celebrated her first birthday Sunday, Feb. 17, with a beautiful cake all for her very own. She is the daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Paul Garcia of 1033 Bustrick Heights. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Conchita Carmen Garcia sticking her finger in her first birthday cake
